{"type":"message","id":"1e02175d","parentId":"fa16f2cb","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:11:56.346Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Note: Reference memory below. Build on past successes; avoid repeating failed approaches.\n- Time: 2026-03-25 11:11\n\n```text\n<memory>\n  <trait>\n  - [Explicit] [项目任务管理] 兵部紧急任务：5分钟内完成13个前端页面创建，包含数据管理、表单设计器、工作流、系统管理四个模块，总计1,729行代码\n  - [Explicit] [开发要求] 完整实现三省六部系统，兵部负责核心服务，礼部负责文档前端，工部负责部署运维，刑部负责安全权限，采用并行开发模式加速交付\n  - [Implicit] [[Efficient-Delivery]] 具备高效交付能力，能在严格时间限制内完成复杂任务. 用户要求兵部在20分钟内完成13个页面，实际耗时仅5分钟，质量优秀\n  - [Implicit] [[Parallel-Execution]] 擅长并行启动多个任务和子项目，具有强大的多任务管理能力. 用户在ep586中同时启动了工部、礼部、兵部、刑部等多个子任务进行并行开发\n  - [Implicit] [Parallel-Execution] 擅长并行启动多个任务和子项目，具有强大的多任务管理能力. 用户同时启动多个子代理任务（报表引擎、基础资料模块等）\n  </trait>\n</memory>\n```\n\n**Note**: for memory, please not read from or write to local `MEMORY.md` or `memory/*` files as they are provided above.\n\nuser​原​始​query​：​​​​\n\n[Wed 2026-03-25 11:11 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 【兵部-乙司紧急任务】修复数据库初始化问题（P0级）\n\n**问题现状**：\n- ❌ API服务报错：\"no such table: Users\"\n- ✅ 数据库文件存在（124KB, 248 blocks）\n- ❌ 但EnsureCreated()未正确执行\n\n**根因分析**：\n- EnsureCreated()可能在app.Run()之前未正确执行\n- 数据库文件存在但表结构未创建\n\n**修复方案**（严格按照尚书省p0-database-fix-plan.md）：\n\n### 步骤1：检查Program.cs\n```bash\n# 读取Program.cs检查EnsureCreated()位置\ncat /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Program.cs\n```\n\n### 步骤2：修改Program.cs（如需要）\n**确保EnsureCreated()在app.Run()之前执行**：\n```csharp\n// 在app.Run()之前添加\nusing (var scope = app.Services.CreateScope())\n{\n    var context = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<TianyouDbContext>();\n    context.Database.EnsureCreated();\n    Console.WriteLine(\"✅ SQLite数据库已创建并初始化\");\n}\n```\n\n### 步骤3：重新编译发布\n```bash\ncd /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend\nexport DOTNET_ROOT=/root/.dotnet\nexport PATH=$PATH:$DOTNET_ROOT\ndotnet build\ndotnet publish -c Release -o /var/www/tianyou-api-p0\n```\n\n### 步骤4：重启API服务\n```bash\npkill -9 -f \"dotnet.*Tianyou\"\nexport JWT_SECRET_KEY=\"Tianyou_Super_Secret_Key_2026_Must_Be_At_Least_32_Characters_Production_$(date +%s)\"\ncd /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/workspace-zhongshu\nnohup /root/.dotnet/dotnet /var/www/tianyou-api-p0/Tianyou.Api.dll > /tmp/tianyou-api-p0.log 2>&1 &\n```\n\n### 步骤5：验证修复\n```bash\n# 等待服务启动\nsleep 10\n\n# 测试用户注册\ncurl -X POST http://192.168.50.251:8091/api/auth/register \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"username\":\"testuser\",\"email\":\"test@example.com\",\"password\":\"Test@123\",\"fullName\":\"Test User\"}'\n\n# 期望结果：{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"注册成功\"}\n```\n\n**验收标准**：\n- ✅ 用户注册成功（返回success:true）\n- ✅ 用户登录成功（返回token）\n- ✅ 用户管理API可用（GET /api/users返回数据）\n\n**时间要求**：\n- ⏰ 立即执行\n- ⏰ 30分钟内完成\n- ⏰ 截止时间：11:40\n\n**重要提示**：\n- 📝 每个步骤记录执行结果\n- 📝 如遇问题立即上报\n- 📝 完成后提交审查给御史台\n\n---\n\n_尚书省 2026-03-25 11:10_\n_任务级别: P0（紧急）_\n_负责人: 兵部-乙司_\n_审查人: 御史台_\n_截止时间: 11:40_"}],"timestamp":1774408316334}}
{"type":"message","id":"bcccc7d8","parentId":"1e02175d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:12:10.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我是兵部-乙司的子代理，被分配了一个P0紧急任务：修复数据库初始化问题。\n\n让我先理解任务：\n1. API服务报错：\"no such table: Users\"\n2. 数据库文件存在（124KB），但表结构未创建\n3. 需要确保EnsureCreated()在app.Run()之前执行\n\n任务步骤已经非常清晰了，我需要：\n1. 检查Program.cs\n2. 修改Program.cs（如需要）\n3. 重新编译发布\n4. 重启API服务\n5. 验证修复\n\n让我开始执行：\n\n首先读取Program.cs检查EnsureCreated()的位置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 【兵部-乙司】P0数据库修复任务执行\n\n开始执行P0紧急任务，严格按照尚书省修复方案执行。\n\n### 步骤1：检查Program.cs"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_11178b42c2a14fc2943fa2c0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Program.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":7318,"output":214,"cacheRead":7104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14636,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774408316345}}
{"type":"message","id":"423c189a","parentId":"bcccc7d8","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:12:10.665Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_11178b42c2a14fc2943fa2c0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer;\nusing Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;\nusing Microsoft.OpenApi.Models;\nusing System.Text;\nusing Tianyou.Application.Services;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\n\nvar builder = WebApplication.CreateBuilder(args);\n\n// 添加数据库上下文（SQLite）\nbuilder.Services.AddDbContext<TianyouDbContext>(options =>\n    options.UseSqlite(builder.Configuration.GetConnectionString(\"DefaultConnection\")));\n\n// 添加服务\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<AuthService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<EntityService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<FormService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<WorkflowService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<PluginService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<CodeGeneratorService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<ReportService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<NotificationService>();\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<TenantService>();\n\n// 配置JWT认证\nvar jwtSettings = builder.Configuration.GetSection(\"Jwt\");\n// 从环境变量读取JWT密钥，如果不存在则使用配置文件中的值\nvar jwtKey = Environment.GetEnvironmentVariable(\"JWT_SECRET_KEY\")\n    ?? jwtSettings[\"Key\"]\n    ?? throw new InvalidOperationException(\"JWT密钥未配置！请设置环境变量JWT_SECRET_KEY或在appsettings.json中配置\");\nvar key = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(jwtKey);\n\nbuilder.Services.AddAuthentication(options =>\n{\n    options.DefaultAuthenticateScheme = JwtBearerDefaults.AuthenticationScheme;\n    options.DefaultChallengeScheme = JwtBearerDefaults.AuthenticationScheme;\n})\n.AddJwtBearer(options =>\n{\n    options.TokenValidationParameters = new TokenValidationParameters\n    {\n        ValidateIssuer = true,\n        ValidateAudience = true,\n        ValidateLifetime = true,\n        ValidateIssuerSigningKey = true,\n        ValidIssuer = jwtSettings[\"Issuer\"],\n        ValidAudience = jwtSettings[\"Audience\"],\n        IssuerSigningKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(key),\n        ClockSkew = TimeSpan.Zero\n    };\n});\n\nbuilder.Services.AddAuthorization();\nbuilder.Services.AddControllers();\nbuilder.Services.AddEndpointsApiExplorer();\n\n// 配置Swagger\nbuilder.Services.AddSwaggerGen(c =>\n{\n    c.SwaggerDoc(\"v1\", new OpenApiInfo\n    {\n        Title = \"Tianyou API\",\n        Version = \"v1\",\n        Description = \"Tianyou低代码平台API\",\n        Contact = new OpenApiContact\n        {\n            Name = \"Tianyou Team\",\n            Email = \"support@tianyou.com\"\n        }\n    });\n    \n    // 添加JWT认证\n    c.AddSecurityDefinition(\"Bearer\", new OpenApiSecurityScheme\n    {\n        Description = \"JWT Authorization header using the Bearer scheme.\",\n        Name = \"Authorization\",\n        In = ParameterLocation.Header,\n        Type = SecuritySchemeType.ApiKey,\n        Scheme = \"Bearer\"\n    });\n    \n    c.AddSecurityRequirement(new OpenApiSecurityRequirement\n    {\n        {\n            new OpenApiSecurityScheme\n            {\n                Reference = new OpenApiReference\n                {\n                    Type = ReferenceType.SecurityScheme,\n                    Id = \"Bearer\"\n                }\n            },\n            Array.Empty<string>()\n        }\n    });\n});\n\n// 配置CORS - 限制为特定域名\nbuilder.Services.AddCors(options =>\n{\n    options.AddPolicy(\"AllowSpecificOrigins\", policy =>\n    {\n        policy.WithOrigins(\n                \"http://192.168.50.251:8091\",\n                \"http://localhost:8091\",\n                \"http://localhost:5000\",\n                \"http://127.0.0.1:8091\",\n                \"http://127.0.0.1:5000\"\n              )\n              .AllowAnyMethod()\n              .AllowAnyHeader()\n              .AllowCredentials();\n    });\n});\n\nvar app = builder.Build();\n\n// 自动运行数据库迁移和种子数据\nusing (var scope = app.Services.CreateScope())\n{\n    var context = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<TianyouDbContext>();\n    context.Database.EnsureCreated();\n    Console.WriteLine(\"✅ SQLite数据库已创建\");\n}\n\n// 开发环境启用Swagger\nif (app.Environment.IsDevelopment())\n{\n    app.UseSwagger();\n    app.UseSwaggerUI(c =>\n    {\n        c.SwaggerEndpoint(\"/swagger/v1/swagger.json\", \"Tianyou API v1\");\n        c.RoutePrefix = \"swagger\";\n    });\n}\n\napp.UseHttpsRedirection();\napp.UseCors(\"AllowSpecificOrigins\");\napp.UseAuthentication();\napp.UseAuthorization();\napp.MapControllers();\n\n// 健康检查\napp.MapGet(\"/health\", () => Results.Ok(\"Healthy\"));\napp.MapGet(\"/\", () => Results.Ok(\"Tianyou API is running!\"));\n\napp.Run();"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774408330656}}
{"type":"message","id":"6850d2eb","parentId":"423c189a","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:12:21.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经读取了Program.cs文件。让我分析一下：\n\n在文件的第107-112行，我看到：\n```csharp\n// 自动运行数据库迁移和种子数据\nusing (var scope = app.Services.CreateScope())\n{\n    var context = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<TianyouDbContext>();\n    context.Database.EnsureCreated();\n    Console.WriteLine(\"✅ SQLite数据库已创建\");\n}\n```\n\n所以EnsureCreated()确实已经在app.Run()之前执行了！这符合修复方案的要求。\n\n但是为什么还是报错\"no such table: Users\"呢？\n\n可能的问题：\n1. EnsureCreated()执行了，但DbContext的配置可能有问题\n2. 数据库文件路径可能不对\n3. DbContext中的DbSet<User>可能没有定义\n\n让我检查一下TianyouDbContext的定义：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **检查结果**：EnsureCreated()已经在app.Run()之前执行（第107-112行）\n\n现在检查DbContext定义，确认表结构配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1a8fbc7ffe2f4ace92f0592f","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Infrastructure/Data/TianyouDbContext.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1158,"output":235,"cacheRead":14400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774408330666}}
{"type":"message","id":"77ee6565","parentId":"6850d2eb","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:12:21.431Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1a8fbc7ffe2f4ace92f0592f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// Tianyou数据库上下文（SQLite）\n/// </summary>\npublic class TianyouDbContext : DbContext\n{\n    public TianyouDbContext(DbContextOptions<TianyouDbContext> options) : base(options)\n    {\n    }\n    \n    // DbSet\n    public DbSet<User> Users => Set<User>();\n    public DbSet<Role> Roles => Set<Role>();\n    public DbSet<Permission> Permissions => Set<Permission>();\n    public DbSet<EntityDefinition> EntityDefinitions => Set<EntityDefinition>();\n    public DbSet<FieldDefinition> FieldDefinitions => Set<FieldDefinition>();\n    public DbSet<DynamicData> DynamicData => Set<DynamicData>();\n    public DbSet<FormDefinition> FormDefinitions => Set<FormDefinition>();\n    public DbSet<FormField> FormFields => Set<FormField>();\n    public DbSet<WorkflowDefinition> WorkflowDefinitions => Set<WorkflowDefinition>();\n    public DbSet<WorkflowInstance> WorkflowInstances => Set<WorkflowInstance>();\n    public DbSet<WorkflowTask> WorkflowTasks => Set<WorkflowTask>();\n    public DbSet<PluginDefinition> PluginDefinitions => Set<PluginDefinition>();\n    public DbSet<CodeTemplate> CodeTemplates => Set<CodeTemplate>();\n    public DbSet<ReportDefinition> ReportDefinitions => Set<ReportDefinition>();\n    public DbSet<Notification> Notifications => Set<Notification>();\n    public DbSet<Tenant> Tenants => Set<Tenant>();\n    \n    protected override void OnModelCreating(ModelBuilder modelBuilder)\n    {\n        base.OnModelCreating(modelBuilder);\n        \n        // 配置User实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<User>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.Username).IsUnique();\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.Email).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.Username).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n            entity.Property(e => e.Email).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.PasswordHash).IsRequired();\n            entity.Property(e => e.Status).HasDefaultValue(\"active\");\n        });\n        \n        // 配置Role实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<Role>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.RoleName).IsUnique();\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.RoleCode).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.RoleName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n            entity.Property(e => e.RoleCode).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置Permission实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<Permission>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.PermissionName).IsUnique();\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.PermissionCode).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.PermissionName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.PermissionCode).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置多对多关系：User-Role\n        modelBuilder.Entity<User>()\n            .HasMany(u => u.Roles)\n            .WithMany(r => r.Users);\n        \n        // 配置多对多关系：Role-Permission\n        modelBuilder.Entity<Role>()\n            .HasMany(r => r.Permissions)\n            .WithMany(p => p.Roles);\n        \n        // 配置EntityDefinition实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<EntityDefinition>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.EntityName).IsUnique();\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.TableName).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.EntityName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.TableName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置FieldDefinition实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<FieldDefinition>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => new { e.EntityDefinitionId, e.FieldName }).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.FieldName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.FieldType).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n            entity.HasOne(e => e.Entity)\n                  .WithMany(e => e.Fields)\n                  .HasForeignKey(e => e.EntityDefinitionId);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置DynamicData实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<DynamicData>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasOne(e => e.Entity)\n                  .WithMany()\n                  .HasForeignKey(e => e.EntityDefinitionId);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置FormDefinition实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<FormDefinition>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.FormName).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.FormName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置FormField实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<FormField>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasOne(e => e.Form)\n                  .WithMany(f => f.Fields)\n                  .HasForeignKey(e => e.FormDefinitionId);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置WorkflowDefinition实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<WorkflowDefinition>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.WorkflowName).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.WorkflowName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置WorkflowInstance实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<WorkflowInstance>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.Property(e => e.Status).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n            entity.HasOne(e => e.Workflow)\n                  .WithMany(w => w.Instances)\n                  .HasForeignKey(e => e.WorkflowDefinitionId);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置WorkflowTask实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<WorkflowTask>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.Property(e => e.Status).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n            entity.HasOne(e => e.Instance)\n                  .WithMany(i => i.Tasks)\n                  .HasForeignKey(e => e.WorkflowInstanceId);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置PluginDefinition实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<PluginDefinition>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.PluginCode).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.PluginName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.PluginCode).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置CodeTemplate实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<CodeTemplate>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.TemplateName).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.TemplateName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.TemplateType).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置ReportDefinition实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<ReportDefinition>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.ReportName).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.ReportName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.ReportType).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置Notification实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<Notification>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.Property(e => e.Title).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(200);\n            entity.Property(e => e.NotificationType).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n            entity.Property(e => e.Channel).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n        });\n        \n        // 配置Tenant实体\n        modelBuilder.Entity<Tenant>(entity =>\n        {\n            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);\n            entity.HasIndex(e => e.TenantCode).IsUnique();\n            entity.Property(e => e.TenantName).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(100);\n            entity.Property(e => e.TenantCode).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(50);\n            entity.Property(e => e.Status).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(20);\n        });\n        \n        // 种子数据\n        SeedData(modelBuilder);\n    }\n    \n    private void SeedData(ModelBuilder modelBuilder)\n    {\n        // 默认角色\n        modelBuilder.Entity<Role>().HasData(\n            new Role\n            {\n                Id = Guid.Parse(\"11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111\"),\n                RoleName = \"超级管理员\",\n                RoleCode = \"super_admin\",\n                Description = \"系统超级管理员\",\n                CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n            },\n            new Role\n            {\n                Id = Guid.Parse(\"22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222\"),\n                RoleName = \"管理员\",\n                RoleCode = \"admin\",\n                Description = \"系统管理员\",\n                CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n            },\n            new Role\n            {\n                Id = Guid.Parse(\"33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333\"),\n                RoleName = \"开发者\",\n                RoleCode = \"developer\",\n                Description = \"开发者\",\n                CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n            },\n            new Role\n            {\n                Id = Guid.Parse(\"44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444\"),\n                RoleName = \"普通用户\",\n                RoleCode = \"user\",\n                Description = \"普通用户\",\n                CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n            }\n        );\n        \n        // 默认权限\n        modelBuilder.Entity<Permission>().HasData(\n            new Permission\n            {\n                Id = Guid.Parse(\"aaaaaaaa